<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to RENT-HUB</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to RENT-HUB!</h1>
        <p>Dear <span class="highlight">{{name}}</span>,</p>
        <p>We are excited to have you on board with the email <span class="highlight">{{email}}</span>. Thank you for registering!</p>
        <p>Get ready to explore amazing rental opportunities and manage your properties effortlessly.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Happy renting,</p>
            <p>The RENT-HUB Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
